text: Antistathmoptera daltonae is a moth in the family Saturniidae described by Tams in 1935. It is found in Tanzania, Malawi, Mozambique, South Africa, Zimbabwe and Zambia. ==Subspecies== *Antistathmoptera daltonae daltonae (Tanzania) *Antistathmoptera daltonae granti Bouyer, 2006 (Tanzania) *Antistathmoptera daltonae rectangulata Pinhey, 1968 (Tanzania, Malawi, Mozambique, South Africa and Zimbabwe) ==References== Category:Saturniinae Category:Moths described in 1935 Category:Moths of Africa
title: Antistathmoptera daltonae
